      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FERREL'S LAW (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a third place finish (16.78) there the start prior. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. GUACAMOLE IRISH (6) last start finished 2nd on May 15 over 300m at this track behind JADED SMILE beaten 2.75 lengths (16.87) in a Grade 5. Can hit the frame with the right run. MY BOY SONNY (1) could manage only sixth at Sandown last time but caught the eye when clocking a sharp 16.80 over 300m at this track the start prior. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. TROPIC MAN (3) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
